    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Exceptionally clean, mint-condition example that presents beautifully inside and out. The paint, interior, and trim all show extremely well, and the car appears to have been very well cared for with minimal visible wear. A standout driver or collector-quality car that a buyer can expect to enjoy immediately without the typical cosmetic or condition compromises.",
