    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Exceptionally clean, well-kept vehicle in mint condition. The exterior presents beautifully, the interior is equally impressive, and it is the kind of car that feels properly cared for throughout rather than just cleaned up for sale. Everything about it shows pride of ownership, and a buyer should expect a turn-key, ready-to-enjoy example with none of the project-car needs suggested by earlier condition.",
