    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Straightforward, affordable transportation with solid value for the right buyer. This vehicle is being offered as-is in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a budget-friendly project, work car, or dependable parts donor. Priced to reflect its condition while still offering an accessible entry point, it\u2019s a practical opportunity for a buyer who knows how to spot potential.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a cheap runabout or a project with potential? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest little machine that still has life left in it. It\u2019s got the kind of character you\u2019d expect from a well-used vehicle, and for the right buyer it could make a handy daily, backup car, or weekend fixer-upper. If you want something affordable without spending a fortune, this is a great chance to grab a car at a sensible price.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly driver/project with a strong-running engine, dependable automatic operation, and a chassis that still feels willing on the road. Cosmetically it shows age and use, but the core mechanical package has good bones and offers a great platform for a daily, backup car, or weekend fixer-upper. If you want affordable transportation with real potential and straightforward serviceability, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Cheap, honest transportation. Rough around the edges, but it runs and gets the job done. Priced to move fast.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A car with honest character and plenty of story left to tell, this is the kind of ride that speaks to drivers who appreciate grit, charm, and possibility. It has the seasoned presence of a machine that\u2019s seen life and still stands ready for its next chapter\u2014whether that\u2019s as a practical around-town companion, a weekend tinkerer's project, or simply an inexpensive set of wheels with personality. If you like vehicles with soul and don\u2019t mind a little rough-around-the-edges attitude, this one offers a lot of opportunity at a budget-friendly entry point.",
      "price": 6500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
